Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:48.32,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,さあ暗を照らせ 今日、阳は无くとも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:54.87,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,呜呼この胸に燃ゆる火よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.85,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,超常の生命に不意に邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.81,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,善悪も际限も知らないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.60,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,御托の前に生存竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:23.14,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,脳と皮肤で感じ取った死线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:27.36,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,踌躇なんて恐怖なんて踏み砕く 大前提のルール
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:33.65,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,梦に缒る脆弱(よわさ)など この星に置き场はなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:40.12,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,朝を生きて迎える为 绝望などここに置いていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.16,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,ヒトよ夸れ热き鼓动を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:46.75,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,霊长类(おれたち)の意志をいま一撃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.46,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,打ち砕け冻る悲しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:52.63,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,魂で叫べその怒りを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.59,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,神が居なくとも祈れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:03:02.35,OP.jp,,0,0,0,,その命　燃やせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:48.32,OP,,0,0,0,,来吧 点亮黑暗 就算今日再无烈日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:54.87,OP,,0,0,0,,啊 这份在我心中熊熊燃烧的火焰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.85,OP,,0,0,0,,不经意间与超乎常理的生命发生邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.81,OP,,0,0,0,,若是难辨善恶 数量无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.60,OP,,0,0,0,,唯有趁废话连篇之前 先进行生存竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:23.14,OP,,0,0,0,,大脑与皮肤所感受到的存亡一线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:27.36,OP,,0,0,0,,将犹豫与恐怖一并踩碎 身处大前提的规则下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:33.65,OP,,0,0,0,,依赖于美梦的脆弱 在这颗星球上找不到容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:40.12,OP,,0,0,0,,为了活着迎接晨曦的到来 就将绝望留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.16,OP,,0,0,0,,人类啊 为自己炙热的心跳自豪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:46.75,OP,,0,0,0,,将灵长类的意志融进此刻的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.46,OP,,0,0,0,,将那冰封的悲伤 全部击碎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:52.63,OP,,0,0,0,,用灵魂呐喊 那一份愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.59,OP,,0,0,0,,就算世上没有神明也祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:03:02.35,OP,,0,0,0,,燃烧自己的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,头还是腿?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我从哪开始?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,印度尼西亚原产
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沙螽总科 超大型昆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sia ferox
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,食性 肉食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:00:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,腿部力量强劲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,性情极其凶猛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会想起这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,09 TOO SAD TO DIE 一粒雷雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,已经都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,已经结束了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,却无法抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,却无法抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是动了心这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是她让我成了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:06:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 我希望...能像你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能像个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 为什么啊 为什么要做那种像动物一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,班长...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不来了?怎么不来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,让我杀了你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,旗...帜?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,班长...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,班长!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,班长 该换班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,灯 你也休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我还能再...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你的身体是经过手术强化的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你也没办法不眠不休地战斗40天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能睡的时候就睡 这也是任务的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老老实实换班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,阿历克斯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 交给我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常理解那家伙的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这异样的宁静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么 正在发生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这一生...都在被人利用...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,伊娃 伊莎贝拉 大家 对不起啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我...不行了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,班长!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,伊娃 快点带班长去四班的逃生机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快点!我们会守住这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,休想!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,每次 每次都是阿道夫班长救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在地球 在火星 都是没用的废物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不对...你们快逃啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这种时候丢下阿道夫班长逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:14:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就真的是人渣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,伊娃!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要保住班长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 用疫苗 救救我的儿子!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,班长...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊...好冷...心脏...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊 班长!!不要啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢生物吗?特别是鱼类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为一般人不会知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,电鳗发电的原理什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊...我也不是自己特意了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只是实验而已...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 只要与我的人生关 不管是什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,AED
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,电击除颤器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,目的是让发生心室颤动的心脏停止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,人的心脏和灵魂就算停止...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不甘心...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只要还有生存下去的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@PMingLiU\pos(227,105)\frz270\an1}不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一定不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伊娃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,恩里克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,珊德拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里茨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,安托尼奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莱西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉皮克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,乔汉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,乔汉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等着 我这就来救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,药...那么大量...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,此时主对摩西说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你向天伸杖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊 班长!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,使埃及遍地的人身上和牲畜身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,并田间各样菜蔬上 都有冰雹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,摩西向天伸杖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,主就打雷下雹 有火闪到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,主下雹在埃及地上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@PMingLiU\pos(126,105)\frz270\an1}这就是\N他的愤怒与悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那时 雹与雷掺杂 甚是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@PMingLiU\pos(126,105)\frz270\an1}这就是\N阿道夫．莱因哈德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@PMingLiU\pos(126,105)\frz270\an1}这就是\N第二位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让路...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,自从埃及成国以来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,遍地没有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,主的神迹如此苛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雷与雹降向埃及全土
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,城乡山川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,几日几夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:21:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雹击打了田间所有的人和牲畜 所有生物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,雹击打了田间一切的菜蔬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,又打坏田间一切的树木
